metadata.name: Over The Rainbow
metadata.description:
Sometimes, after a long gallop on my magic unicorn, I find myself in a remote, desolate region. There are no fairy-tale creatures, no connection with the outside world, all the channels are on forced rest.
I linger a little there, sometimes longer, sometimes shorter time, I think just so for that I don't forget how privileged I am, that I can generally have adventures in my imagination without limits...
